*SPEF "IEEE 1481-1998"
*DESIGN "top"
*DATE "Mon Jan 1 00:00:00 2026"
*VENDOR "synthetic"
*PROGRAM "spef_def_names"
*VERSION "1.0"
*DESIGN_FLOW "MISSING_NETS"
*DIVIDER /
*DELIMITER :
*BUS_DELIMITER [ ]
*T_UNIT 1.0 PS
*C_UNIT 1.0 PF
*R_UNIT 1.0 OHM
*L_UNIT 1.0 HENRY

*PORTS
in I
out O

*D_NET in 0.300
*CONN
*P in I
*I b_plain:A I *L .003
*I cts\/leaf_buf:A I *L .003
*I bus\[0\]:A I *L .003
*CAP
1 in 0.10
2 b_plain:A 0.05
3 cts\/leaf_buf:A 0.05
4 bus\[0\]:A 0.05
*RES
5 in b_plain:A 50
6 in cts\/leaf_buf:A 50
7 in bus\[0\]:A 50
*END

*D_NET n_plain 0.250
*CONN
*I b_plain:Z O
*I b_sink_a:A I *L .003
*CAP
1 b_plain:Z 0.10
2 b_sink_a:A 0.05
*RES
3 b_plain:Z b_sink_a:A 50
*END

*D_NET cts\/leaf_net 0.250
*CONN
*I cts\/leaf_buf:Z O
*I b_sink_b:A I *L .003
*CAP
1 cts\/leaf_buf:Z 0.10
2 b_sink_b:A 0.05
*RES
3 cts\/leaf_buf:Z b_sink_b:A 50
*END

*D_NET bus_n\[0\] 0.250
*CONN
*I bus\[0\]:Z O
*I b_sink_c:A I *L .003
*CAP
1 bus\[0\]:Z 0.10
2 b_sink_c:A 0.05
*RES
3 bus\[0\]:Z b_sink_c:A 50
*END
